OOC: Sounds good.  One came from Perplex's ship.  And just who is this 
"injured bot"?  I missed that at some point.

::Aerotaur::
    He knew he was falling but there was nothing he could do about it.  His 
vision blurred and he blacked out.  As he hit the floor he vaguely heard 
Nightlight say his name.  While in the CR chamber he dreamt of many things.  
He dreamt of the battles he had been in.  He dreamt of the people he knew.
